From 0f668a23934648303c1ed18d2e441a669bba9909 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: fi3 <email@email.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 16:32:46 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 2/4] ADD Vim-style terminal visual selection for focused pane
 yanks

Terminal users need a modal copy path that matches the focused pane. Character, line, and block visual selections share the existing TerminalUi frame path, while terminal adapters and the UI harness use the same yank extraction so right-pane transcripts, prompts, and left-pane rows copy consistently.
---
